"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>rad</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>kolumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>markör</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

