msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>rad</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>kolumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>markör</"
